{"tid":483421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有病唔好番工？】衛生署報告：八成人有病不請假　六成無求醫","createTime":"2017-11-29T06:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T10:35:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dac419e1e22a07e9dc7a7e965412b2903fb645ba","tid":483421,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171129/s00001/39323e4af31e34290338d354ea8acb5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171129%2Fs00001%2F39323e4af31e34290338d354ea8acb5b.jpg&h=8d3f7b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「有病就唔好番工番學喇！」政府宣傳片口號人人琅琅上口，但衛生署最新人口健康調查發現，於調查前30天內患病的受訪者中，近六成人沒有就診，八成人都沒有請病假。<br />\n<br />\n衛生署發表2014/15年度人口健康調查報告書，於2014年12月至2015年10月期間訪問了12,022名15歲或以上人士，五成七人表示於調查前30天內，患有傷風、關節痛、高膽固醇、高血壓、糖尿病、視力及聽力健康等急性疾病或健康問題，當中女性（61.4%） 比男性（52.1%）更可能出現健康問題。<br />\n<br />\n不過調查發現，有健康問題的受訪者中，57.6%沒有就診，53.7%沒有接受治療，82%更沒有請病假。<br />\n<br />\n調查又發現，48%受訪者在調查前30天出現睡眠困擾，包括難以入眠（30分鐘內無法入睡）、間歇睡醒或早醒後無法再入睡，男女比例分別為43.7%及51.9%。以睡眠困擾頻率計算，一周3次或以上難以入眠、間歇睡醒及早醒後無法在入睡的比率，分別為6.8%、7.3%及6%，當中女性所佔比率較高。<br />\n<br />\n精神科醫生曾繁光表示，市民習慣臨睡前玩手機或平板電腦，屏幕發出的「藍光」會令大腦誤以為是日間，同樣影響睡眠質素。他又說，睡眠困擾通常是情緒、行為出現問題的警號，若持續一兩周睡得不好，應及時向精神科醫生求醫。<br />\n<br />\n另外，調查發現，在調查前一年內曾有自殺意念的受訪者佔1.2%，當中青年比例最高，15至24歲有2.6%曾想自殺，有2.1萬人。至於曾嘗試自殺佔想自殺者的8.9%，當中6100人試過4次自殺或以上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171129/s00001/1511923820436\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171129%2Fs00001%2F1511923820436&d=jQ8xyZDsqHejrt5cQn20JMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1f199351\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171129%2Fs00001%2F1511923820436&h=216a52a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171129/s00001/1511923820436</a>"},{"pid":"794a7614ce12cd835cdf79408cf25295f57d0e21","tid":483421,"uid":133529,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:21:14.000Z","msg":"剩低個兩成都係公務員"},{"pid":"983844f7736d09c87e1d6db3bf9a8d00319204f3","tid":483421,"uid":26672,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:23:07.000Z","msg":"八成人有病唔<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">俾</span></span>請假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ce5abe34bc7420be57d1bc97ac169d55b3f2e9","tid":483421,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"一大堆精神有問題嘅打工仔唔敢求醫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50dea21f87778af557c93d46ae9472020f32d91","tid":483421,"uid":46943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"請病假人八成無病"},{"pid":"2e50de38b3ad4acd2bdc43f66b40380ff39da77d","tid":483421,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"哪有錢你老母.jpg"},{"pid":"9b2147695209f741b1fcc7ca5efbf85886dc5cf3","tid":483421,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:29:23.000Z","msg":"請多幾日就俾人照肺，不如你立例管下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3606bee730348f4f896aaf65fe82264b8c461e6e","tid":483421,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母打去普通科門診預約難過登天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b80e75a7d6f6cda7706c0977c9f41f398d0c31a","tid":483421,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:36:56.000Z","msg":"請假又要扣人工，街症又排唔到，私家就閒閒地三四佰埋單，你養我全家啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94749180c5394f56a44b62e4f18b5fb1a6f424eb","tid":483421,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母打去普通科門診預約難過登天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要門診無聯網，番工遠啲book唔到就近門診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbeaf5faaaa9f2cf8260d0f26f9188179c68d8e","tid":483421,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:45:04.000Z","msg":"唔撚使做咩屌你老母<br />\n又扣人工 又要比錢睇"},{"pid":"24b9a35a611be903ff7cde44f34618c87249f3cb","tid":483421,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"你估我想病咩 屌你老母仆街老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142862f6779368ae13987111a0e090452f12df16","tid":483421,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母打去普通科門診預約難過登天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要門診無聯網，番工遠啲book唔到就近門診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n次次book都比埋d 垃圾時間我<br />\n正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係逼人去急症室姐<br />\n打電話又打到手都軟"},{"pid":"c5fd21c4b4282bff3661bf99cb5954061d76d4db","tid":483421,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:59:49.000Z","msg":"番私人工照樣乜鳩都請假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司醫保睇一次都係15蚊"},{"pid":"b2f1c70641cb2d5879a8c57685f95f06172c2c0e","tid":483421,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"請完病假就炒<br />\n請病假扣人工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5c84707b03f89d1fae751c5497e89900628abf","tid":483421,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"r